data.name: Urdu's Qmoeva
data.notes: "Urdu's Qmoeva" is active for just a very short time from midnight until dawn in ganglion antropolis in Cauldros. To find it enter ganglion antropolis under FN Site 505, head over the arched bridge with the marnucks and puglith and turn right to find more marnucks and Urdu's Qmoeva. Complete the Definian Downfall mission to gain access to ganglion antropolis.
